attrs.script:
-- https://github.com/moltenform/vipercard
-- re-created in ViperCard by Ben Fisher

on startNewGameState
	global curLevel, numLives, maxGridX, maxGridY
	global curScore
	put 40 into maxGridX -- not 30
	put 40 into maxGridY -- not 22
	put 1 into curLevel
	put 3 into numLives
	put 0 into curScore
	repeat with lvl = 1 to 6
		put (lvl-1)+2975 into idYou
		set the showLabel of cd btn id idYou to false
		set the autoHilite of cd btn id idYou to false
		set the style of cd btn id idYou to \
			"transparent"
		set the name of cd btn id idYou to \
			"spacegameSprites_n_you"
		set the rect of cd btn id idYou to 1,1,18,18
		
		put (lvl-1)+3005 into idOxygenFull
		set the showLabel of cd btn id idOxygenFull to \
			false
		set the autoHilite of cd btn id idOxygenFull to \
			false
		set the style of cd btn id idOxygenFull to \
			"rectangle"
		set the rect of cd btn id idOxygenFull to \
			5, 47, 5+83, 47+10
		
		put (lvl-1)+3011 into idOxygenCurrent
		set showLabel of cd btn id idOxygenCurrent to \
			false
		set autoHilite of cd btn id idOxygenCurrent to \
			false
		set style of cd btn id idOxygenCurrent to \
			"rectangle"
		set rect of cd btn id idOxygenCurrent to \
			5, 47, 5+83, 47+10
		set hilite of cd btn id idOxygenCurrent to \
			true
		
		set the rect of cd btn id idYou to 1,1,18,18
		put (lvl-1)+2981 into idStatus
		set style of cd fld id idStatus to "transparent"
		set the top of cd fld id idStatus to 5
		set the left of cd fld id idStatus to 5
		set the lockText of cd fld id idStatus to true
		put "" into cd fld id idStatus
		
		put (lvl-1)+2992 into idStartPos
		hide cd btn id idStartPos
		put (lvl-1)+2998 into idNewGame
		show cd btn id idNewGame
		set the rect of cd btn id idNewGame to \
			5, 65, 5+83, 65+33
		set the name of cd btn id idNewGame to \
			"startNewGame"
		set the label of cd btn id idNewGame to \
			"Exit Game"
		
	end repeat
	
	global cKey, cPltf, cPts, cRamp, cTank, cDoorTop
	global cDoorBtm, cChute
	put 13 into cKey
	put 1 into cPltf
	put 7 into cPts
	put 5 into cRamp
	put 6 into cTank
	put 14 into cDoorTop
	put 15 into cDoorBtm
	put 8 into cChute
	
	play "spacegame_1_airlock" load
	play "spacegame_1_bonus" load
	play "spacegame_1_boot" load
	play "spacegame_1_cannon" load
	play "spacegame_1_chute" load
	play "spacegame_1_extra" load
	play "spacegame_1_fry" load
	play "spacegame_1_jump" load
	play "spacegame_1_materialize" load
	play "spacegame_1_nooxy" load
	play "spacegame_1_scream" load
	play "spacegame_1_splat" load
	play "spacegame_1_spring" load
	play "spacegame_1_walk" load
end startNewGameState

on updateScoreStatus
	global curLevel, curScore, numLives, curOxy
	if curLevel is "" then
		exit updateScoreStatus
	end if
	
	put (curLevel-1)+2981 into idStatus
	put "Score: " & curScore & " Lives: " & numLives \
		into cd fld id idStatus
	
	put (curLevel-1)+3005 into idOxygenFull
	put (curLevel-1)+3011 into idOxygenCurrent
	set the width of cd btn id idOxygenFull to 100
	set the width of cd btn id idOxygenCurrent to \
		round(max(1, curOxy/(300/100)))
end updateScoreStatus

-- we use the positions of the buttons as level data
-- this way, you can easily edit a level by moving the 
-- buttons around
-- because the grid size is 14pixels x 14 pixels, 
-- we can convert from
-- pixel position to grid position by dividing by 14.

on loadLevel
	global curLevel, numLives, curOxy, curGrid
	global maxGridX, maxGridY, meGridX, meGridY, hasKey
	global cKey, cPltf, cPts, cRamp, cTank, cDoorTop
	global cDoorBtm, cChute
	global keysNeeded, doorsNeeded
	global itemLookups
	put "" into curGrid
	set the itemDelimiter to ","
	put 0 into hasKey
	
	put 300 into curOxy
	put 0 into keysNeeded
	put 0 into doorsNeeded
	
	put "" into templateLine
	repeat with y = 1 to maxGridX
		put 0 into item y of templateLine
	end repeat
	repeat with x = 1 to maxGridY
		put templateLine into line x of curGrid
	end repeat
	
	put 1928+172*(curLevel-1) into basisId
	put "" into itemLookups
	repeat with x = basisId to basisId + 172-3
		if the icon of cd btn id x is not 0 then
			show cd btn id x
			put the icon of cd btn id x into whatType
			put trunc((the left of cd btn id x)/14) into \
				gridX
			put trunc((the top of cd btn id x)/14) into \
				gridY
			
			put line gridX of curGrid into curLine
			put whatType into item gridY of curLine
			put curLine into line gridX of curGrid
			
			if whatType is cKey or whatType is cPts or \
				whatType is cTank or \
					whatType is cDoorBtm then
				put "" into itemLookup
				put whatType into item 1 of itemLookup
				put "1" into item 2 of itemLookup
				put x into item 3 of itemLookup
				put gridX into item 4 of itemLookup
				put gridY into item 5 of itemLookup
				put itemLookup & cr after itemLookups
			end if
			if whatType is cKey then
				add 1 to keysNeeded
			end if
			if whatType is cDoorBtm then
				add 1 to doorsNeeded
			end if
		end if
	end repeat
	
	put (curLevel-1)+2992 into idStartPos
	put trunc((the left of cd btn id idStartPos)/14) \
		into meGridX
	put trunc((the top of cd btn id idStartPos)/14) \
		into meGridY
	
	put (curLevel-1)+2975 into idYou
	set the icon of cd btn id idYou to 40+1
	set the left of cd btn id idYou to meGridX*14
	set the top of cd btn id idYou to meGridY*14
	updateScoreStatus
end loadLevel

on moveYou dir
	global curLevel, numLives, curOxy, curGrid
	global maxGridX, maxGridY, meGridX, meGridY
	global hasKey, cheatFloat, justBeatLevel
	global cKey, cPltf, cPts, cRamp, cTank, cDoorTop
	global cDoorBtm, cChute
	if curLevel is "" then
		exit moveYou
	end if
	
	global itemLookups
	put (curLevel-1)+2975 into idYou
	put 1 into canSurviveFall
	if cheatFloat is not "" then
		-- completely override movement, 
		-- the floating cheat is on.
		if dir is 1 then
			add 1 to meGridX
		else if dir is -1 then
			subtract 1 from meGridX
		else if dir is 10 then
			subtract 1 from meGridY
		else if dir is -10 then
			add 1 to meGridY
		end if
		
		put item meGridY of (line meGridX of curGrid) \
			into isThere
		set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
			meGridX*14, meGridY*14
		
		put 0 into justBeatLevel
		checkItemGet isThere
		if justBeatLevel is 1 then
			onBeatLevel
			exit moveYou
		end if
		updateScoreStatus
		exit moveYou
	end if
	
	if dir is 1 or dir is -1 then
		-- you pressed left or right
		subtract 1 from curOxy
		put meGridX+dir into destx
		put meGridY into desty
		put item (desty) of (line destx of curGrid) \
			into isThere
		if isThere is cPltf then
			-- can't walk into a platform
			exit moveYou
		end if
		
		-- do animation
		if dir is 1 then
			set the icon of cd btn id idYou to 30+1
			set the left of cd btn id idYou to meGridX*14 + 7
			wait 50 ms
			set the icon of cd btn id idYou to 40+1
			set the left of cd btn id idYou to destx
		else
			set the icon of cd btn id idYou to 31+1
			set the left of cd btn id idYou to meGridX*14 - 7
			wait 50 ms
			set the icon of cd btn id idYou to 41+1
			set the left of cd btn id idYou to destx
		end if
		put destx into meGridX
		put desty into meGridY
	else if dir is 100 then
		-- you pressed jump
		subtract 3.75 from curOxy
		
		-- hop one up and two across
		if (the icon of cd btn id idYou) mod 2 is 0 then
			put -1 into jumpDir
		else
			put 1 into jumpDir
		end if
		put meGridX into tempDestX
		put meGridY - 1 into tempDestY
		put item tempDestY of \
			(line tempDestX of curGrid) into isThere
		if isThere is cPltf then
			exit moveYou
		end if
		
		put meGridX + 1*jumpDir into tempDestX
		put meGridY - 1 into tempDestY
		put item tempDestY of \
			(line tempDestX of curGrid) into isThere
		if isThere is cPltf or isThere is cRamp then
			exit moveYou
		end if
		
		put meGridX + 2*jumpDir into tempDestX
		put meGridY - 1 into tempDestY
		put item tempDestY of \
			(line tempDestX of curGrid) into isThere
		put false into minijump
		if isThere is cPltf or isThere is cRamp then
			-- we can still do it, 
			-- we'll just do a minijump
			put true into minijump
		end if
		
		-- play sound + animation
		play "spacegame_1_jump"
		put meGridX into tempDestX
		put meGridY - 1 into tempDestY
		set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
			tempDestX*14, tempDestY*14
		wait 50 ms
		put meGridX + 1*jumpDir into tempDestX
		put meGridY - 1 into tempDestY
		set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
			tempDestX*14, tempDestY*14
		
		if not minijump then
			wait 50 ms
			put meGridX + 2*jumpDir into tempDestX
			put meGridY - 1 into tempDestY
			set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to tempDestX*14, tempDestY*14
		end if
		put 3 into canSurviveFall
		put tempDestX into meGridX
		put tempDestY into meGridY
	else if dir is 10 then
		-- you pressed up
		subtract 1 from curOxy
		put item meGridY of \
			(line meGridX of curGrid) into isThere
		
		-- if you are stuck inside a platform,
		-- presumably you are coming up from a ramp
		if isThere is cRamp or isThere is cPltf  then
			put meGridY-1 into meGridY
			set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
				meGridX*14, meGridY*14
		else
			exit moveYou
		end if
	else if dir is -10 then
		-- you pressed down
		subtract 1 from curOxy
		put item (meGridY+1) of \
			(line meGridX of curGrid) into isThere1
		put item (meGridY+2) of \
			(line meGridX of curGrid) into isThere2
		if isThere1 is cRamp or isThere2 is cRamp then
			put meGridY+1 into meGridY
			set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
				meGridX*14, meGridY*14
		else
			exit moveYou
		end if
	end if
	
	-- see if there's an item/key/door
	put item meGridY of (line meGridX of curGrid) \
		into isThere
	put 0 into justBeatLevel
	checkItemGet isThere
	if justBeatLevel is 1 then
		onBeatLevel
		exit moveYou
	end if
	if isThere is cChute then
		put 100 into canSurviveFall
	end if
	
	-- loop, you are falling downwards
	repeat
		-- did you end up on solid ground?
		put item (meGridY+1) of \
			(line meGridX of curGrid) into isThereBeneath
		if isThereBeneath is cPltf or \
			isThereBeneath is cRamp then
			
			exit repeat
		else if isThereBeneath is cChute then
			put 100 into canSurviveFall
		end if
		if meGridY >= maxGridY then
			exit repeat
		end if
		
		-- keep falling
		put meGridY+1 into meGridY
		subtract 1 from canSurviveFall
		set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
			meGridX*14, meGridY*14
		wait 50 ms
	end repeat
	
	set the topLeft of cd btn id idYou to \
		meGridX*14, meGridY*14
	
	if canSurviveFall < 0 then
		play "spacegame_1_splat"
		set the icon of cd btn id idYou to 65+1
		beginDeath
	else if meGridY >= (maxGridY-3) then
		play "spacegame_1_scream"
		beginDeath
	else if curOxy <= 0 then
		play "spacegame_1_nooxy"
		wait 400 ms
		beginDeath
	end if
	updateScoreStatus
end moveYou

on beginDeath
	global curLevel, numLives, curOxy, curGrid
	global maxGridX, maxGridY, meGridX, meGridY
	global hasKey, curScore
	
	wait 50 ms
	subtract 1 from numLives
	if numLives <= 0 then
		put "" into curLevel
		answer ("Game Over" & cr & cr & \
			"Score: " & curScore)
		go to cd 1
	else
		loadLevel
		updateScoreStatus
	end if
end beginDeath

on onBeatLevel
	global curLevel, numLives, curOxy, curGrid
	global maxGridX, maxGridY, meGridX, meGridY
	global hasKey, curScore
	put curLevel + 1 into curLevel
	if curLevel > 6 then
		answer ("You beat the game! Score " & curScore)
		put "" into curLevel
		go to cd 1
		exit onBeatLevel
	end if
	go to cd (curLevel + 1)
	loadLevel
	add 200 to curScore
	updateScoreStatus
end onBeatLevel

on checkItemGet isThere
	global curLevel, numLives, curOxy, curGrid
	global maxGridX, maxGridY, meGridX, meGridY
	global hasKey, curScore, justBeatLevel
	global cKey, cPltf, cPts, cRamp, cTank
	global cDoorTop, cDoorBtm, cChute
	global keysNeeded, doorsNeeded
	
	global itemLookups
	repeat with x = 1 to the number of lines in itemLookups
		put line x of itemLookups into theLine
		put item 4 of (theLine) into gridX
		put item 5 of (theLine) into gridY
		if gridX is meGridX and gridY is meGridY and \
			(item 2 of theLine is "1") then
			-- we found an item!
			put true into gettingIt
			put item 1 of theLine into whatType 
			if whatType is cKey then
				play "spacegame_1_chute"
				add 1 to hasKey
			else if whatType is cPts then
				play "spacegame_1_extra"
				add 100 to curScore
			else if whatType is cTank then
				play "spacegame_1_extra"
				add 50 to curScore
				add 75 to curOxy
				put min(300, curOxy) into curOxy
			else if whatType is cDoorBtm then
				if hasKey <= 0 then
					put false into gettingIt
					answer "key needed."
				else
					subtract 1 from hasKey
					subtract 1 from doorsNeeded
					if doorsNeeded <= 0 then
						play "spacegame_1_bonus"
						put 1 into justBeatLevel
					else
						play "spacegame_1_airlock"
					end if
				end if
			end if
			
			-- delete the item since 
			-- it's not there anymore
			if gettingIt then
				put "0" into item 2 of theLine
				put theLine into line x of itemLookups
				hide cd btn id (item 3 of theLine)
			end if
		end if
	end repeat
end checkItemGet

on afterKeyDown
	global curLevel, lastDirPressed, cheatInvincible
	global numLives, cheatFloat
	if keyRepeated() then
		exit afterKeyDown
	end if
	if curLevel is "" then
		exit afterKeyDown
	end if
	
	if keychar() is "ArrowLeft" then
		moveYou -1
	else if keychar() is "ArrowRight" then
		moveYou 1
	else if keychar() is "ArrowUp" then
		moveYou 10
	else if keychar() is "ArrowDown" then
		moveYou -10
	else if keychar() is " " then
		moveYou 100
	else if keyChar() is "T" and shiftKey() and \
		not keyRepeated() then
		answer "cheatcode:float"
		if cheatFloat is not "" then
			put "" into cheatFloat
		else
			put "1" into cheatFloat
		end if
	else if keyChar() is "X" and shiftKey() and \
		not keyRepeated() then
		answer "going to next level"
		onBeatLevel
	else if keyChar() is "L" and shiftKey() and \
		not keyRepeated() then
		answer "cheatcode:new life"
		add 1 to numLives
		
	else if keyChar() is "I" and shiftKey() and \
		not keyRepeated() then
		answer "toggle cheatcode:invincible"
		if cheatInvincible is true then
			put false into cheatInvincible
		else
			put true into cheatInvincible
		end if
	end if
	updateScoreStatus
end afterKeyDown

on mouseUp
	if "startNewGame" is in the short name of \
		the target then
		go to cd 1
	end if
end mouseUp

attrs.script:
on mouseUp
	answer ("To edit any level, choose the button " & \
		"tool. Then, Go to the next card to " & \
		"move to the first level. You can now click a" & \
		" platform or item to select and move it. " & \
		"To play the level, choose the browse (hand) tool, " & \
		"click " & "Exit Game, and then click New Game.")
end mouseUp
